<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="43">Not seen. Protologue: &quot;Italia, in Valle Bisagno prope Genuam, loco Prato, supra rupem calcaream colore fuscorufo tinctam. leg. Sbarbaro, 1946&quot;.</paragraph>
